Modifications made:
- Replaced Google Gemini API with local GGUF model inference using node-llama-cpp
- Added Trust framework integration for privacy-focused local-first AI
- Added comprehensive model management and verification features
- Added performance monitoring and hardware optimization
- Added privacy modes with data sanitization and encryption
- Added MCP (Model Context Protocol) server compatibility for local models
- Added streaming responses and chat history management
- Added Git integration and workflow automation
- Added benchmarking tools and JSON schema enforcement
- Rebranded as Trust CLI for local-first AI workflows
- Implemented complete test suite for production readiness
- Updated copyright notices to Audit Risk Media LLC
- Maintained Apache 2.0 license while ensuring proper attribution

